<p>John and Dave have a great discussion today answering your questions, sharing your tips, and more. Topics include tweaking Safari&rsquo;s settings to load your custom tabs, resolving IR remote issues, an excellent primer on using Terminal Commands, Resetting mobileMe, and more. Subscribe today, support your two favorite geeks, and enjoy!</p>
<p>Note: Shownotes are complete!</p>
